        "<p>And have grown most uncommonly fat;</p>\n<p>Yet you turned a back-somersault in at the doorâ€”</p>\n<p>Pray, what is the reason of that?â€</p>\n<p>â€œIn my youth,â€ said the sage, as he shook his grey locks,</p>\n<p>â€œI kept all my limbs very supple</p>\n<p>By the use of this ointmentâ€”one shilling the boxâ€”</p>\n<p>Allow me to sell you a couple?â€</p>\n",
