        "<p>Her chin was pressed</p>\n<p>so closely against her foot, that there was hardly room to open her</p>\n<p>mouth; but she did it at last, and managed to swallow a morsel of the</p>\n<p>lefthand bit.</p>\n<p>*      *      *      *      *      *      *</p>\n<p>*      *      *      *      *      *</p>\n<p>*      *      *      *      *      *      *</p>\n",
