        "<p>â€œIs that the reason so many</p>\n<p>tea-things are put out here?â€ she asked.</p>\n<p>â€œYes, thatâ€™s it,â€ said the Hatter with a sigh: â€œitâ€™s always tea-time,</p>\n<p>and weâ€™ve no time to wash the things between whiles.â€</p>\n<p>â€œThen you keep moving round, I suppose?â€ said Alice.</p>\n<p>â€œExactly so,â€ said the Hatter: â€œas the things get used up.â€</p>\n<p>â€œBut what happens when you come to the beginning again?â€ Alice ventured</p>\n",
