        "<p>and sadly:â€”</p>\n<p>â€œWill you walk a little faster?â€ said a whiting to a snail.</p>\n<p>â€œThereâ€™s a porpoise close behind us, and heâ€™s treading on my tail.</p>\n<p>See how eagerly the lobsters and the turtles all advance!</p>\n<p>They are waiting on the shingleâ€”will you come and join the dance?</p>\n<p>Will you, wonâ€™t you, will you, wonâ€™t you, will you join the dance?</p>\n<p>Will you, wonâ€™t you, will you, wonâ€™t you, wonâ€™t you join the dance?</p>\n",
