        "<p>No accounting for tastes!</p>\n<p>Sing her â€˜_Turtle Soup_,â€™ will you, old</p>\n<p>fellow?â€</p>\n<p>The Mock Turtle sighed deeply, and began, in a voice sometimes choked</p>\n<p>with sobs, to sing this:â€”</p>\n<p>â€œBeautiful Soup, so rich and green,</p>\n<p>Waiting in a hot tureen!</p>\n",
