        "<p>On this the White Rabbit blew three blasts on the trumpet, and then</p>\n<p>unrolled the parchment scroll, and read as follows:â€”</p>\n<p>â€œThe Queen of Hearts, she made some tarts,</p>\n<p>All on a summer day:</p>\n<p>The Knave of Hearts, he stole those tarts,</p>\n<p>And took them quite away!â€</p>\n<p>â€œConsider your verdict,â€ the King said to the jury.</p>\n",
