        "<p>Iâ€™m a hatter.â€</p>\n<p>Here the Queen put on her spectacles, and began staring at the Hatter,</p>\n<p>who turned pale and fidgeted.</p>\n<p>â€œGive your evidence,â€ said the King; â€œand donâ€™t be nervous, or Iâ€™ll</p>\n<p>have you executed on the spot.â€</p>\n<p>This did not seem to encourage the witness at all: he kept shifting</p>\n<p>from one foot to the other, looking uneasily at the Queen, and in his</p>\n",
